Dar Al Arkan to Seek 2 Billion Riyals Loan for Khozam Project

-- B y   S h a j i   M a t h e w
-- 
2011-10-09T12:59:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-09/dar-al-arkan-to-seek-2-billion-riyals-loan-for-khozam-project.html
Dar Al Arkan Real Estate Development
Co. (ALARKAN) ,  Saudi Arabia ’s biggest property company by assets, said it
would seek 2 billion riyals from commercial banks and other
entities to develop the Qasr Khozam project.  Total financing required for the joint-venture project in
Jeddah is 6 billion riyals, and the government’s Public
Investment Fund will provide 4 billion riyals, Dar Al Arkan said
in a statement to the Saudi bourse today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shaji Mathew in Dubai at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bruce Stanley at 
 bstanley5@bloomberg.net  